        "content": "<p>Mark-Simulacrum opened <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13715\">PR #13715</a> from <code>Mark-Simulacrum:hint-generics</code> to <code>bytecodealliance:main</code>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>This fixes compilation with the new trait solver (probably an upstream<br>\nbug, haven't checked, but this is a trivial workaround). See compilation<br>\nfailure here: <a href=\"https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/pull/157590#issuecomment-4772783906\">https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/pull/157590#issuecomment-4772783906</a>.</p>\n<p>This hinting is already present for other calls to the same function (search for <code>add_to_linker_instance::</code> in the edited file).</p>\n<p>If possible, it would be great to get this released in a patch release of v46.</p>\n</blockquote>",
